    narr:generatedFrom "fd721ccf348291f1579109a8b073e09299ddd262" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolution of aswritten's brand identity, centering on the [finalized tagline](narr:Position_TaglineFinalized) established in March 2026. The current positioning relies on a two-beat structure—trust through human source, proof through AI citation—which serves as the anchor for ongoing pitch development across [creation](narr:Obs_Tagline_Layer1), [architecture](narr:Obs_Tagline_Layer2), and [infrastructure](narr:Obs_Tagline_Layer3) layers. While the core tagline is settled, the hub remains a site of active experimentation, with recent drafts exploring [conversational hero narratives](narr:Position_LandingPageTagline_Jul2026) and specific sales-motion coinages like [reachability without interruptability](narr:StyleObs_ReachabilityPhrase). The identity work is deeply informed by the [Elephant Collective](narr:Narrative_ElephantCollective) lineage, which treats narrative as a founder's weapon, and is governed by a rigorous set of [rhetorical style rules](narr:StyleObs_4), including the use of [all-caps emphasis](narr:StyleObs_AllCapsEmphasis) and [antithetical framing](narr:StyleObs_SII_ThreeAxisAntithesis) to assert authority. The trajectory is marked by [explicit supersessions](narr:Position_TaglineSupersession), such as the rejection of the \"phone number\" metaphor in favor of \"curated expertise installation.\"""" ;
